This paper discusses the evaluation of password advice, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper discusses the user experience and human-computer interaction aspects of password advice (cs.HC). The paper also touches upon the social implications of password advice and the need for a cultural shift in password creation (cs.SI). The paper also discusses the implementation of password advice, which falls under the category of cybersecurity (cs.CY) and software engineering (cs.SE).
